snippet.title: Amber Heard: 'Incredibly painful' to relive breakup with Jonny Depp
snippet.description:
Amber Heard said reliving "the most traumatic and intimate details" of her life with Jonny Depp was "incredibly painful".

In a statement on the last day of the libel trial, Heard stood by her testimony and placed her "faith" in the British justice system as both sides wait for the judge's ruling.

She said the lawsuit was taking up "precious resources" and would be glad to see them re-allocated to "more important matters" delayed by COVID-19.
